        "action": "Don\u2019t allow affordability checks for sports betting",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The Government should ban bookmakers from conducting affordability checks on bettors. Bettors shouldn\u2019t have to experience intrusive checks covering aspects of their finances. The Government should also abandon its proposals for frictionless checks that they\u2019ve included in the recent white paper.",
